snippet.textDisplay: Finally Annural Khalid features in coke studio, it shouldve been last season, but better late than never, i predicted it last year on one of her song. Its a very different song for what she usually sings, so something new with a combo of Maanu makes it a nice song, but there is too much going on in the video, distracting from the song and somehow the music is louder than the voices. I think CS team should pull back a bit on the visuals and focus on the main feature, i.e. the talented singers and musicians.
